    <keyword>SMTP</keyword>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The objective of Simple Mail Transfer Protocol (SMTP) is to transfer mail reliably and efficiently.  SMTP is independent of the particular transmission subsystem and requires only a reliable ordered data stream channel.  Obsoletes RFC 788, 780, and 772.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
